<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong> “三文鱼大满贯刺身拼盘” </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一整盘一共<strong>17件</strong>厚切三文鱼，<strong>折后才30+</strong>！蕉仔都觉得老板简直是crazy man！ </p>
